            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-col">
            <div class="skill-label">
              <span class="lng-en">Visualization &amp; Tools</span>
              <span class="lng-es">Visualización y Tools</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-items">
              <span>D3.js</span>
              <span>HTML Canvas</span>
              <span>Google Maps API</span>
              <span>Lottie</span>
              <span>Python</span>
